oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Simon Says State Finals
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); Restrikes;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (brown, green, and dark green on beige) announcing the Simon Says State Finals on June 8. Poster features a woodcut of a man. This poster was reprinted in 2005 and 2007. Posters printed after the original edition are known as "restrikes."
